ructure that are poor fits to NFW profiles and those ``bridged'' by the\n(isodensity-based)FOF algorithm. A closer investigation of the bridged halos\nreveals that the fraction of these halos and their satellite mass distribution\nis cosmology dependent. (abridged)\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 26 Mar 2008 02:12:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-06-23"}
