w results with\nprevious work on Local Group galaxies we obtain a new flux weighted gravity\nluminosity relationship (FGLR), which is very well defined and appears to be an\nexcellent alternative tool to determine distances to galaxies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 26 Mar 2008 01:00:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
